		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It looks really nice! Congratulations on finishing this project. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> <br /><br />One nitpick i have is that the &quot;NES-001&quot; font and size seems a little out of context for me. I'd probably put a small sized serif and/or monospace font just shy within the margins of a corner, but that's just me and tastes vary.<br />And maybe call it CHR-RAM/ROM on the cartridge side since it varies. Maybe PPU SRAM instead of VID SRAM.<br /><br />I'd assume the Game Boy might be a logical step from there?

		

